attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a rolling cart. They begin by taking off the wheels, then the top and middle tray. They organize the hardware, then take off the bottom tray and stack the trays. Next, they unscrew the screws from the side bars, then the lower screws of the side bars. Finally, they disassemble the base frame.
